snippet.title: Kryxivia Trailer 15/02/2022 - Master
snippet.description:
Trailer of the upcoming MMORPG game Kryxivia - https://kryxivia.io/ 

Directed by Studio Tattooin Beat
Illustration: Quentin Dognon
Animation: Pierre Lafouge
Music & Sound Design: Rémi Agullo & Emile Boudghene
